      <title>泰国说，它将Uyghurs送回了中国，以避免北京的反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/thailand-says-it-sent-uyghurs-back-to-china-to-avoid-backlash-from-beijing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国上周捍卫了将40名Uyghur被拘留者驱逐出境，是避免北京反弹的“最佳解决方案”，此举违反了国际法，而返回者可能会面临酷刑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/thailand-says-it-sent-uyghurs-back-to-china-to-avoid-backlash-from-beijing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 07:29:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国房价边缘降低，因为急于打败税收截止日期淡出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/uk-house-prices-edge-lower-in-february-halifax-data-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据抵押贷款人哈利法克斯（Halifax）的说法，英国房价在2月下跌，这表明急于击败关键税收截止日期即将结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/uk-house-prices-edge-lower-in-february-halifax-data-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 07:07:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
