    <item>
      <title>韩国法院说，元总统可以离开监狱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/south-korean-president-yoon-to-be-released-from-jail-ytn-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国法院已决定将总统Yoon Suk Yeol从监狱中释放出来，这有可能为这位弹each领导人提供了罕见的胜利，因为他在等待是否应该对他是否应该从办公室罢免他对戒严法的简短施加判决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/south-korean-president-yoon-to-be-released-from-jail-ytn-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 05:10:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普批评与日本的安全条约不平等</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-criticizes-security-treaty-with-japan-as-uneven</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）周四批评了美国 - 日本安全条约，强调了一个事实，即美国有义务根据协议捍卫日本，但日本也没有提供相同的安全保证作为回报，即使是从贸易关系中获得东京的利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-criticizes-security-treaty-with-japan-as-uneven</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 02:43:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普行政命令后，比特币下降使市场失望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-signs-order-creating-bitcoin-reserve-and-crypto-stockpile</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统签署了一项期待已久的命令后，加密货币行业中的镇压紧张局势浮出水面，创造了战略性的比特币储备和其他数字资产的额外库存。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-signs-order-creating-bitcoin-reserve-and-crypto-stockpile</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 00:54:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
